        {
            "title": "英國通膨降至10個月低點 為英國央行進一步降息提供依據",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Office for National Statistics\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"693\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UIeRl5NuMl2rsiocMI7RCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5Mw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5bce47d7751ab5dbaa6b2d25e175d3d8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Office for National Statistics</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國通膨降至自2025年3月以來的最低水平，強化了英國央行下月降息的理由。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國國家統計局周三表示，1月消費者價格同比上漲3%，低於上月的3.4%，彼時通膨受波動性因素影響而短期推高。1月數據符合經濟學家預期，略高於英國央行預測的2.9%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">汽油價格下跌對通膨尤其有拖累作用。機票和食品價格同樣對CPI造成下行壓力，抵消了酒店價格上漲的影響。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"693\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/46_MGYOl31RC7u0VU0Ymhw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5Mw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/eb4d517eaf32ade27692c2ab4a2d0337\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為衡量本土物價壓力的重要指標，服務業通膨降至4.4%，略高於經濟學家預期的4.3%和英國央行預測的4.1%。核心通膨升至3.1%，高於央行預期的2.9%，但仍為2021年以來的最低水平。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5a920657-70f2-31b5-bd24-43c26ea48915-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">商品通膨在一定程度上抵消了服務和核心通膨中仍存的黏性物價壓力。商品通膨從2.2%大幅下降至1.6%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣市場維持降息預期不變，預計今年將有兩次各25個基點的降息，其中第一次可能最快在下月實施。英鎊兌美元小幅下跌0.1%，報1.356。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次通膨數據是英國央行3月19日利率會議前的最後一期數據公佈。央行預計，隨著財政大臣Rachel Reeves於11月預算中宣布的措施逐步對生活成本產生影響，CPI有望在春季回到2%的目標水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題UK Inflation Falls to 10-Month Low as BOE Mulls Further Cuts (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Mark Evans、Harumi Ichikura、Joel Rinneby、Sylvia Westall、Alice Gledhill.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
